    front: "State Roll's spread estimator in terms of observed transaction price autocovariance.",
    back: "Spread s = 2·√(−Cov(Δpₜ, Δpₜ₋₁)). Only valid when the autocovariance is negative — positive autocovariance signals momentum/info effects breaking the model.",
